<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-52-1230 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper describes a heat recovery and utilization technique and systemdesigned for implementation in the gas-fueled heat treatment furnacesof a number of industrial engine and automotive plants in the SovietUnion. Specific implementation and design strategies are given for differenttypes of furnaces in use. Energy savings and cost benefits are analyzed.</TEXT></DOC>